Review Text: I have ordered kaju biryani but they didn't provide curry and onions also, they only provided curd.Its really not good, please think about customers their problem while they taking dinner without curry and onions and lemon.
Ordered mutton curry.its worse. I have decided not to order once again from this mahalaxmi kite when once again . My dear mahalaxmi kitchen please give importance to customers

Quality of the food is not up to the mark specially roti are mostly uncooked and overpriced.
Sorry to make you upset but cannot rate more than this...

I ordered paneer butter masala along with phulka. Paneer Butter Masala was as good as its cost but the phulka was not upto the mark. It felt like plain chapati which we can get in Rs 6 each at local outlets. The restaurant should either improve the quality or lower the price of phulka.

Couldn't ate egg fried rice... With tomato sauce.
Upset with the taste. This is my honest rating from my end. Hope u would try to make it better...
